The Only "System Design" Cheatsheet YOU NEED !!
========================================

I have compiled 50 Most Asked "System Design" Interview questions along with the companies where they were asked. Here are some of them -

1) Design a distributed caching and monitoring system.
Company's asked - Google, Meta, Amazon, eBay, Datadog, Atlassian

2) Design a distributed Stream Processing System like Kafka.
Company's asked - Amazon, Microsoft, Wise, COnfluent

3) Design Dropbox or Google Drive
Company's Asked - Microsoft, Meta, Qualtrics

4) Design an ETA Service and Location Sharing between Driver and Rider
Company's Asked - Uber, Lyft

5) Design a Hotel Booking System: Room Availability, Reservation, Booking
Company's asked - Amazon, Booking dot com

6) Design a Price Alert System for Amazon (or other Stock Prices)
Company's asked -  Meta, Bloomberg, Coinbase, Binance

7)  Design a System to Monitor the Health of a Kubernetes Cluster
Company's Asked - Uber, Lacework, Amazon, Google

8) Design a distributed Botnet
Company's Asked - Meta, Lyft

9) Design a live comment feature for Instagram/Meta.
Company's Asked - Meta, Youtube

10) Design Whatsapp/Telegram.
Company's Asked - Amazon, Microsoft, Oracle, Apple
